<form action="#" method="POST" class="registration-form"> <p class="form-intro">
    Compila il modulo sottostante per richiedere l'iscrizione. Verrai ricontattato via email per la conferma e i dettagli di fatturazione.
  </p>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="nome">Nome</label>
    <input type="text" id="nome" name="nome" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="cognome">Cognome</label>
    <input type="text" id="cognome" name="cognome" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="email">Email</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="telefono">Telefono</label>
    <input type="tel" id="telefono" name="telefono" required>
  </div>
   <div class="form-group privacy-consent">
        <input type="checkbox" id="privacy" name="privacy" value="accepted" required>
        <label for="privacy">
            Ho letto e accetto l'<a href="/privacy" target="_blank">Informativa sulla Privacy</a> e i <a href="/termini" target="_blank">Termini del Servizio</a>.
        </label>
   </div>
  <button type="submit">Invia Richiesta</button>
   <p class="form-note">
       Nota: L'attivazione del servizio e la fatturazione verranno gestite manualmente via email dopo la verifica della richiesta.
   </p>
</form>

<style>
   .registration-form {
     max-width: 600px;
     margin: 0 auto;
     padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
     border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
     border-radius: 8px;
     background-color: var(--light-gray);
   }
   .form-intro, .form-note {
     margin-bottom: var(--spacing-unit);
     font-size: 0.95rem;
     color: var(--secondary-color);
   }
    .form-note {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-unit);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .privacy-consent {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start; /* Align checkbox with start of label */
        gap: 0.5rem; /* Space between checkbox and label */
        margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 1.5);
    }
    .privacy-consent input[type="checkbox"] {
       margin-top: 0.2em; /* Align checkbox better with text */
       flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevent checkbox shrinking */
    }
    .privacy-consent label {
       font-weight: normal; /* Make privacy label normal weight */
       margin-bottom: 0; /* Remove default label margin */
       font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .privacy-consent label a {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
    button[type="submit"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 0.8) 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
</style>